}}</ref><ref>{{статья|автор=COL (Ret) Victor M. Rosello, Col. (Ret) David Shunk, COL Michael D. Winstead.|заглавие=The relevance of technology in Afghanistan|издание=Field Artillery|издательство=HQDA PB6-89-2|год=2011|номер=September-October|pages=56}}</ref>.

